Agent Assisted Loan Application for Digital Lending

Bankers can assist applicants complete their loan application using the agent assisted loan application process. Use Product Catalog Management to show bankers the loan products for which an applicant is eligible. Bankers can assist a client with a loan application process, view contextual information, and have access to relevant tasks by using Digital Lending Omnistudio components.
